#JWT 
json web token
used to manage user session

JWT has following items
header,payload,signature. 

- > JWT by default use 'HS256' algorithm for encryption 

jwt usage in nodejs : 
  to send user information as token
  to manage session (user don't have to authenticate again and again.)
  we can set token expiry (eg : 15m)

